0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"［無政府狀態］元朗恐怖襲擊將成民間自治催産士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fb32276ab013436b6fbc73349d613cad4e1605d","tid":1345813,"uid":28432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:49:24.000Z","msg":"如果有媒體誤會白衫人係反送中示威者 一定要幫手澄清 唔該各位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439d60297033772ed9a1c3afeaf80f723fe98ef5","tid":1345813,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"有冇講埋本應係10分鐘內到嘅差佬2個鐘都唔見? 仲有3間警署落閘? 呢D先係有數據質疑差佬喎, D鬼佬不嬲習慣一頭半個鐘先見差佬."}]}